find one if she was pure in heart.

00:46:17.192 --> 00:46:19.653
And I'm pure
in heart, right?

00:46:20.696 --> 00:46:22.072
The purest.

00:46:26.535 --> 00:46:30.038
Can we stop talking now?
I need to get to sleep.

00:46:30.205 --> 00:46:31.373
Good night, sweetie.

