Wow! That was crazy.
Whoa!

00:53:58.737 --> 00:54:00.906
That was totally
humiliating.

00:54:01.072 --> 00:54:03.992
Taking a bite of that cheese was the
stupidest thing I've ever done.

00:54:04.159 --> 00:54:05.493
Why did I listen
to you?

00:54:05.660 --> 00:54:07.495
Right. But it's over
now, so...

